Collins was married to Marjorie Weinman from 1970 to 1978.
In 1985, he married actress Faye Grant, whom he had met on the set of Tales of the Gold Monkey in 1982.
They separated in 2012, and, after 30 years of marriage, a final divorce decree was issued in January 2015.

In October 2014, the New York City Police Department began investigating Collins after an audio tape leaked to the media revealed a male voice—purported to be that of Collins—admitting to past sexual abuse of a minor under the age of 14.
